  {
    public int AutoID { get; set; }
    // ... other properties matching SQL query columns
  }
}
```

**Key Points**:
- âś… Use `@using NonFactors.Mvc.Grid;`
- âś… Model is `tbl_XXXX_FULL_partial` with `id` + `Items`/`Modelo` properties
- âś… Use `Html.Grid(Model.Items).Build(columns => {...})`
- âś… Use `.UsingSourceUrl()` for AJAX reload
- âś… Use `.Empty()` for no-data message
- âś… Use `.Id()` for grid HTML ID
- âś… Use `Html.ActionLink()` with CSS class for delete actions
- âś… Query returns `IQueryable<tbl_XXXX_FULL>` via `.ToArray().ToList().AsQueryable()`
- âťŚ NEVER create manual `<table>` HTML
- âťŚ NEVER use `IEnumerable<dynamic>` as model
- âťŚ NEVER use `@model` other than the `_FULL_partial` wrapper

